        <p>
            <MadCap:snippetText src="../Users/Users1.flsnp" />
            <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="General.OnlineLive"> See <MadCap:xref href="../../../Users/About_Users.htm">About Users</MadCap:xref> and <MadCap:xref href="../../../Users/Adding_Users.htm">Adding Users</MadCap:xref>.</MadCap:conditionalText>
        </p>
        <p>
            <img src="../../Images/add_users1.png" alt="" title="" class="MaxWidth100Percent">
            </img>
        </p>
        <MadCap:pageBreak MadCap:conditions="CentralGuides.CentralGettingStartedGuide" />
        <p>Users can be added one at a time or in bulk by pointing to a CSV file containing each person’s email, first name, then last name.</p>
        <p>
            <img src="../../Images/add_users2.png" alt="" title="" class="MaxWidth100Percent" />
        </p>
        <p>
            <img src="../../Images/add_users3.png" alt="" title="" class="MaxWidth100Percent">
            </img>
        </p>
        <MadCap:pageBreak MadCap:conditions="CentralGuides.CentralGettingStartedGuide" />
        <p>
            <MadCap:snippetText src="../Users/Users2.flsnp">
            </MadCap:snippetText>
            <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="General.OnlineLive"> See <MadCap:xref href="../../../Users/Setting_Permissions.htm">Setting User Permissions</MadCap:xref>.</MadCap:conditionalText>
        </p>
        <p>
            <img src="../../Images/add_users4.png" alt="" title="" class="MaxWidth100Percent" />
        </p>
        <MadCap:pageBreak MadCap:conditions="CentralGuides.CentralGettingStartedGuide" />
        <p>When a new user is invited, that person receives an email. The individual must click a link to complete their invitation to Central. This allows them to confirm or edit their name, and set up a password. After they submit their information, their account is activated.</p>
        <p>
            <img src="../../Images/confirm_account.png" alt="" title="" class="MaxWidth100Percent" />
        </p>
        <MadCap:pageBreak MadCap:conditions="CentralGuides.CentralGettingStartedGuide" />
        <p>From the Users page, you can see all other users in the system, view their profiles, and contact them. Users with a blue crown icon have “User Administration” permission.</p>
        <p>
            <img src="../../Images/user_card.png" alt="" title="" class="MaxWidth100Percent">
            </img>
        </p>
        <MadCap:pageBreak MadCap:conditions="CentralGuides.CentralGettingStartedGuide" />
        <p>If you click your name at the top of the interface, you can open the Settings dialog to complete your own profile and choose notifications.</p>
        <p>
            <img src="../../Images/settings1.png" alt="" title="" class="MaxWidth85Percent" />
        </p>
        <p>
            <img src="../../Images/settings2.png" alt="" title="" class="MaxWidth85Percent" />
        </p>
    </body>
</html>